This file contains information about the installation process of
Olena. Make sure you have read the BUILD file first.

Please read the README file for general information about Olena.

INSTALLING
==========

To install 
utilities on your system, run

  make install

from the build directory.

If not overriden with `--prefix' (see the BUILD file), this will
install:

   * the headers in `/usr/local/include/oln',
   * utilities in `/usr/local/bin',
   * sample images in '/usr/local/share/oln',
   * the autoconf helper oln.m4 in `/usr/local/share/aclocal'.


